@startuml
!define ICONS /Users/iworldafric/dev/diagrams/plantuml-stdlib/stdlib/tupadr3
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/brain.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/cog.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/cogs.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/list.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/check_circle.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/shield_alt.puml
!include ICONS/common.puml

skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #4A235A
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #7D3C98
skinparam ActivityFontColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActivityFontSize 13
skinparam ActivityArrowColor #C39BD3
skinparam ActivityArrowFontColor #1C2833
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #1A5276
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #2980B9
skinparam ActivityDiamondFontColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActivityStartColor #2ECC71
skinparam ActivityEndColor #E74C3C
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam RoundCorner 12
skinparam Padding 8

title Deliberation Engine — Data Flow

start

:<$brain> **Task Description**
Receive task from Goal Stack:
{ description, priority, constraints, deadline };

:<$cogs> **Task Decomposition**
Break into ordered sub-task list.
Identify dependencies between sub-tasks.
Estimate complexity class per sub-task;

while (sub-tasks remaining?) is (yes)
  :<$list> **Action Proposal**
  Select next eligible sub-task from queue.
  Generate candidate action via Claude API.
  Apply tool pre-selection heuristics;

  :<$cog> **State Prediction**
  Feed action to State Predictor model.
  Predict resulting environment state.
  Estimate confidence and risk score;

  :<$shield_alt> **State Evaluation**
  Score predicted state vs goal criteria.
  Apply constraint checker (budget, scope, safety).
  Compare with alternative action proposals;

  :<$check_circle> **Error Monitoring**
  Query Episodic Memory for similar past failures.
  Adjust confidence based on failure patterns.
  Apply risk-weighted discount factor;
endwhile (no)

:<$brain> **Action Selection**
Select highest-scored action for each sub-task.
Assemble into executable Action Plan.
Dispatch to Execution Engine;

stop
@enduml
